{"tid":2174582,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"（考古）有冇人記得夏美的一步","createTime":"2020-08-26T03:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T21:30:59.000Z","uid":124400,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d93e41dc4e287ecabdff50d64657f1458bb63b52","tid":2174582,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:25:03.000Z","msg":"幾多年前已經唔記得，只記得當年呢段Flash片突然係各大論壇傳播，當時有好多人分析呢段片背後隱藏左好多野，當中好多細思極恐嘅細節，真相並唔係影片睇到咁開心咁治癒。<br />\n<br />\n相關作品好似只有三部：<br />\n<br />\n第一部： <a href=\"http://koshiandoh.com/flash-gallery01/natsumi-step/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkoshiandoh.com%2Fflash-gallery01%2Fnatsumi-step%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=6954b1b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://koshiandoh.com/flash-gallery01/natsumi-step/</a><br />\n制作十分精良，睇完好治癒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K5qS0y8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK5qS0y8.png&h=009ce726&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jfw3nPc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjfw3nPc.png&h=da9d7b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二部: <a href=\"http://koshiandoh.com/flash-gallery01/natsumi-step/naki.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkoshiandoh.com%2Fflash-gallery01%2Fnatsumi-step%2Fnaki.htm&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=e2888d46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://koshiandoh.com/flash-gallery01/natsumi-step/naki.htm</a> 呢段片得20秒左右，入面嘅夏美眼濕濕好似好淒涼好多野想講咁，段片播完會彈個&quot;End&quot;，呢個時候右鍵點擊段片，選擇Play -&gt; 就會有隱藏野出現。當年好多人俾佢嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3kRbwKx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3kRbwKx.png&h=f9b1da20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三部:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ySdUGw9WAY0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DySdUGw9WAY0&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=c03d82d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ySdUGw9WAY0</a><br />\n原片我搵唔到，呢段片好似係同人作品，不過做得非常之好，大概講左成個故事嘅來龍去脈<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以wiki: <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%8F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25A4%258F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25AD%25A5&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=27b7185c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%8F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5</a>"},{"pid":"c80895638dbe43fabfabf3f889df0ff10d98ada2","tid":2174582,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"你講起先記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好詭異既片"},{"pid":"5be71b468d5ec43b8da8df5782eaf8f910168357","tid":2174582,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:43:13.000Z","msg":"仲有如月車站"},{"pid":"694bfd812992bd756649783ccac88a49670b2d46","tid":2174582,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563c08bfcc0719e512f128190c9822bc5cab23d0","tid":2174582,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5be71b468d5ec43b8da8df5782eaf8f910168357","tid":2174582,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:43:13.000Z","msg":"仲有如月車站"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱啱睇左好恐怖"},{"pid":"a48d0180294876eb0b71dfed9e4b41a050753e02","tid":2174582,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:50:07.000Z","msg":"原來有第三部？<img src=\"/assets/faces/